15,01 One of the main reasons I smoke dope is the relaxation and clarity of
15,01purpose it provides.
15,01 This sometimes leads to problems as you can easily become fixated on
15,01useless tasks such as figuring out how big the surface area of two small
15,01pizzas is, and the relation of that figure to seemingly more momentous
15,01issues, such as one's sex life.
15,01 I myself can speak from such experience. Why, I recall a girl, in 1949 I
15,01believe it was, whose bodily features resembled nothing so much as not one,
15,01small pizza, but two! Or was it one?
15,01 Anyways, women and pizza metaphors exist in today's society. First one's
15,01free. Everybody's doing it. But you can always learn to adapt.
15,01 The pizza/women metaphor can be used to explain many of women's so-called
15,01"emotions" (our scientists have discovered that these are not true emotions,
15,01just penial reduction techniques).
15,01 "Ah, Fuck!!!! Who the hell wants to know the history of pizza and women?"
15,01said the author. "I don't think I am cut out to write history texts." He got
15,01up and walked to the kitchen. "Food," he thought. "How easy it must be to
15,01write about." So he got every pot and every pan he had, and set about
15,01learning to cook.
15,01 First off, he decided, he needed to invent his own spice. Just something
15,01to separate him from the rest of the chefs.
15,01 He started with chemical componants.....


